title: Let's get you an agent so you can let the searching be done for you!
posting_body: ['Thanks for visiting my ad!', 'Are you tired of searching aimlessly online for a place?', 'Exhausted?', 'Head is going to burst?', 'If you answered yes to any one of those questions you need to call/text me now!', 'I work to find folks Houses/Condos and apartments in Austin and surrounding and would love to be your agent on your next home!', 'My service is FREE folks, and I work with integrity with all my clients as a fiduciary.', 'If you pick up that 1000 pound phone and give me a call/text, you just saved yourself anxiety, panic, and home search depression!', 'Look forward to helping you with all your housing needs!', '(Wow this could be a prescription drug commercial LOL)', '--Text', 'show contact info', 'to inquiry on my FREE service--', '–Let me know your budget, ideal location, and move in date in the text!--', '–Expect the BEST service, because that is what you deserve–', '--Scott Petermann--HomeSmith Realty--Austin Board of Realtors--10 year Veteran–']
